0area's%20recreational%20opportunities.%20She%20was%20never%20in%20a%20rush%20to%20finish%20tasks%20before%20it%20got%20too%20cold%20or%20snowy%20in%20the%20winter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAround%202016%2C%20she%20also%20started%20to%20see%20the%20political%20atmosphere%20of%20her%20area%20change.%20People%20became%20more%20aggressive%2C%20people%20would%20sell%20political%20shirts%20with%20hateful%20slogans%20on%20them%20on%20many%20street%20corners%2C%20and%20there%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bwave%20of%20animosity%26quot%3B%20that%20made%20her%20question%20whether%20she%20should%20go%20running%20or%20biking%20by%20herself.%20Her%20district%20also%20started%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fflaglerlive.com%2Fbook-bans-flagler-county%2F%23gsc.tab%3D0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebanning%20books%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20she%20said%20was%20one%20of%20the%20final%20straws%20for%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20she%20felt%20lonelier%20in%20her%20area%2C%20and%20by%20extension%2C%20the%20peace%20she%20found%20in%20nature%20was%20no%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EVermont%20pros%20and%20cons%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKim%20and%20her%20husband%20knew%20they%20wanted%20to%20move%20back%20to%20New%20England%20to%20feel%20more%20at%20home%2C%20but%20she%20thought%20Maine%20was%20too%20pricey%20and%20New%20Hampshire%20wasn't%20the%20right%20fit.%20She%20settled%20in%20Berlin%2C%20which%20has%20a%20population%20of%204%2C000%20and%20she%20said%20was%20calmer%20and%20more%20diverse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20buying%20a%20big%20home%2C%20given%20their%20small%20retirement%20income%2C%20Kim%20and%20her%20husband%20decided%20to%20buy%20a%20mobile%20home.%20The%20average%20home%20price%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.realtor.com%2Frealestateandhomes-search%2FMontpelier_VT%2Foverview%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMontpelier%20area%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20around%20%24350%2C000%2C%20and%20since%20they%20couldn't%20afford%20the%20mortgage%2C%20they%20spe