3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20when%20viewing%20the%20home%20in%20Windsor%2C%20England%2C%20she%20came%20through%20an%20entrance%20to%20the%20grounds%20with%20a%20view%20of%20the%20lake%20and%20the%20house%20in%20the%20distance%2C%20and%20in%20that%20moment%2C%20decided%20on%20taking%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20previously%20owned%20by%20a%20Russian%20family%20whose%20children%20were%20at%20Lambrook%20School%2C%20Michelle%20added.%20It's%20the%20same%20school%20Kate%20Middleton%20and%20Prince%20William's%20three%20children%2C%20Prince%20George%2C%20Princess%20Charlotte%2C%20and%20Prince%20Louis%2C%20attend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20previous%20owners%20spent%20a%20few%20weeks%20a%20year%20at%20the%20home%2C%20so%20Michelle%20said%20the%20condition%20had%20deteriorated%20by%20the%20time%20she%20bought%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20home%20is%20vast%2C%20but%20each%20corner%20has%20been%20filled%20with%20treasures%20of%20the%20past.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20entryway%20with%20black%20walls%20and%20antique%20furniture.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655f46a64ca513d8242e09fb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMichelle%20is%20passionate%20about%20antiques.%3Cp%3ESam%20Davis%20Photography%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20home%20has%20seven%20bedrooms%2C%20six%20bathrooms%20(five%20of%20which%20are%20en-suite)%2C%20a%20cloakroom%2C%20a%20utility%20room%2C%20a%20kitchen%2C%20a%20dining%20room%2C%20and%20a%20bar%20%E2%80%93%20which%20Michelle%20has%20named%20%26quot%3Bthe%20pub%26quot%3B%20in%20true%20British%20tradition.%20Other%20features%20include%20two%20living%20rooms%2C%20a%20kitchenette%2C%20a%20lake%2C%20a%20pond%2C%20a%20pool%2C%20a%205-acre%20garden%2C%20and%20a%204.5-acre%20paddock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20having%20so%20much%20space%20to%20fill%2C%20no%20detail%20in%20the%20home%20has%20been%20left%20untouched%20by%20Michelle%20who%20enjoys%20interior%20design%20and%20renovation%20of%20old%20homes.%20This%20is%20the%20seventh%20home%20she%20has%20renovated%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20told%20BI%20she%20loves%20old%20things%2C%20and%20that%20it%20was%20important%20to%20her%20to%20keep%20the%20charm%20of%20the%20home%2C%20which%20was%20built%20in%201520.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EEverything%20used%20in%20the%20house%20is%20old%20or%20antique%20to%20fit%20the%20aesthetic%20of%20the%20building.%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20side%20by%20side%20of%20a%20bathroom%20renovation%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655f45149c7d23cb3b9f309e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20drastic%20transformation%20in%20one%20of%20five%20ensuite%20bathrooms.%3Cp%3ESam%20Davis%20Photography%2C%20Agatha%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20renewed%20it%20in%20a%20way%20that%20fits%20in%20with%20an%20old%20house.%20Part%20of%20the%20charm%20of%20having%20an%20old%20house%20is%20to%20carry%20on%20with%20the%20way%20it%20should%20look%2C%26quot%3B%20Michelle%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhistoricengland.org.uk%2Fadvice%2Fyour-home%2Fowning-historic-property%2Flisted-building%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrade%20II%20listed%3C%2Fa%3E%20home%2C%20meaning%20each%20time%20Michelle%20wanted%20to%20change%20something%20in%20the%20property%2C%20she%20had%20to%20apply%20for%20special%20permission%20from%20her%20local%20authority.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey're%20still%20in%20the%20process%20of%20renovating%20and%20she%20told%20BI%20the%20next%20big%20project%20to%20tackle%20is%20the%20gym%2C%20which%20is%20being%20converted%20from%20a%20carport.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichelle%20said%20she%20plans%20to%20decorate%20it%20with%20workout%20magazine%20cutouts%20from%20the%201920s%20and%20'30s%2C%20and%20is%20currently%20searching%20for%20old%20frames%20to%20put%20these%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20kitchen%20was%20once%20a%20dining%20room%20and%20required%20a%20lot%20of%20work.%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20British%20countryside%20kitchen%20with%20wide%20windows%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655f45cb9c7d23cb3b9f30ba%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20kitchen.%3Cp%3ESam%20Davis%20Photography%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMichelle%20told%20BI%20it%20hasn't%20all%20been%20plain%20sailing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20was%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20moving%20kitchens%2C%20the%20mess%20was%20everywhere%20%E2%80%93%20it%20was%20colossal.%20I%20thought%20never%2C%20ever%20again%20am%20I%20doing%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichelle%20added%20that%20though%20the%20original%20dining%20room%20was%20beautiful%2C%20she%20wanted%20to%20convert%20it%20into%20the%20kitchen%20as%20that's%20where%20people%20are%20likely%20to%20spend%20time%20every%20day%20and%20not%20only%20on%20special%20occasions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20beams%20in%20the%20kitchen%20were%20painted%20black%2C%20but%20once%20this%20had%20been%20done%2C%20Michelle%20felt%20the%20original%20charm%20was%20lost%20so%20she%20had%20it%20sanded%20down%20to%20emulate%20natural%20wear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EA%20priest's%20vestibule%2C%20costing%20around%20%2416%2C000%2C%20was%20transformed%20into%20the%20kitchen%20island.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20original%20priest's%20vestibule%20before%20it%20was%20converted%20into%20a%20kitchen%20island.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655f807a22cf74a5739bfc75%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20original%20priest's%20vestibule%20before%20it%20was%20converted%20into%20a%20kitchen%20island.%3Cp%3EAgatha%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMichelle%20went%20to%20an%20antique%20fair%20called%20Henley%20Decor%20Fair%20where%20she%20found%20a%20vestibule%2C%20a%20chest%20where%20priests%20keep%20their%20garments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20the%20seller%20had%20interest%20from%20other%20buyers%2C%20but%20the%20size%20meant%20most%20people%20had%20no%20space%20for%20it%20in%20their%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichelle%20told%20BI%20she%20had%20already%20ordered%20her%20kitchen%20island%20but%20after%20learning%20she%20could%20cancel%20it%20without%20being%20charged%2C%20she%20took%20a%20chance%20on%20the%20antique%20piece.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20cost%20a%20lot%20of%20money.%20Buying%20the%20vestibule%20cost%20%C2%A35%2C500%2C%26quot%3B%20Michelle%20told%20BI%2C%20which%20is%20around%20%246%2C900.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20only%20half%20the%20battle%20%E2%80%94%20she%20then%20had%20to%20find%20a%20carpenter%20who%20would%20take%20on%20this%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20vestibule%20was%20customized%20to%20be%20a%20functional%20kitchen%20island%2C%20which%20included%20adding%20a%20dishwasher.%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20country%20style%20kitchen%20with%20black%20beams%20and%20old%20wooden%20island.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656f3a5c58e7c0c29a29a66e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20kitchen%20island%20was%20a%20big%20project%20in%20the%20house.%3Cp%3ESam%20Davis%20Photography%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40agathas.uk%2Fvideo%2F7284907023832010017%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETikTok%3C%2Fa%3E%20posted%20to%20Michelle's%20account%20in%20October%20shows%20the%20before%20and%20after%20of%20the%20mammoth%20project%20of%20transforming%20the%20antique%20vestibule%20into%20a%20kitchen%20island.%20It%20has%204.6%20million%20views%20as%20of%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20single%20part%20had%20to%20be%20taken%20apart%20and%20numbered%20because%20I%20didn't%20want%20any%20new%20wood%20involved%20in%20it.%20I%20loved%20that%20it%20had%20a%20history%2C%26quot%3B%20Michelle%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20vestibule%20was%20customized%20to%20be%20functional%20as%20a%20kitchen%20island%2C%20including%20adding%20a%20marble%20countertop%2C%20deep%20drawers%20for%20large%20pots%20and%20pans%2C%20a%20dishwasher%2C%20and%20a%20sink.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20it%20cost%20more%20to%20build%20the%20island%20with%20the%20vestibule%20than%20to%20order%20a%20new%20one%2C%20but%20it%20has%20added%20a%20wow%20factor%20to%20the%20kitchen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMichelle%20is%20a%20seasoned%20renovator%20of%20old%20homes%2C%20and%20sold%20her%20last%20two%20to%20American%20buyers.%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20paddock%20with%20sheep%20running.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655f48be4ca513d8242e0a5d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20home%20comes%20with%20an%20over%204%20and%20a%20half%20acre%20field.%3Cp%3ESam%20Davis%20Photography%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMichelle%20told%20BI%20she%20sold%20the%20last%20two%20homes%20she%20renovated%20to%20American%20buyers%20looking%20for%20their%20dream%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20did%20a%20house%20about%2010%20years%20ago%2C%20it%20was%20falling%20apart%20but%20the%20lady%20who%20bought%20it%20wanted%20everything%20%E2%80%94%20all%20my%20old%20silver%20teapots%2C%20my%20cushions%2C%20my%20curtains.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20for%20her%20current%20home%2C%20which%20she%20plans%20to%20sell%20when%20the%20renovations%20are%20complete%2C%20she%20is%20happy%20to%20sell%20it%20as%20seen%2C%20minus%20one%20chandelier%20which%20she's%20attached%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20benefit%20of%20old%20t