20width%3D%5C%221660%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lines%20at%20Pollo%20Campero%20in%20North%20Carolina%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65677d3fc58b6f84123b6880%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221245%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELines%20at%20Pollo%20Campero%20when%20it%20opened%20last%20year%20in%20North%20Carolina.%3Cp%3EPollo%20Campero%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELos%20Angeles%20area%20news%20helicopters%20captured%20the%20excitement%20of%20the%20day.%20Sales%20hit%20%241%20million%20after%20the%20first%2022%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20frenzy%20over%20the%20brand%2C%20Pollo%20Campero%20has%20grown%20slowly%20in%20the%20US%20over%20the%20last%2020%20years.%20Today%2C%20they%20have%20less%20than%20100%20restaurants%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20US%20expansion%20has%20ramped%20up%20in%20the%20last%20year.%20The%20chain%20has%20also%20added%20new%20items%20to%20its%20US%20menu%2C%20such%20as%20macaroni%20and%20cheese%20and%20chicken%20sandwiches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20US%2C%20Campero%20serves%20pressure-cooked%20fried%20chicken%2C%20empanadas%2C%20a%20spicy%20chicken%20sandwich%2C%20grilled%20chicken%2C%20nuggets%2C%20salads%2C%20rice%20bowls%2C%20rolls%2C%20tortillas%2C%20and%20unique%20sides%20and%20beverages%20such%20as%20plantains%2C%20yuca%20fries%2C%20and%20horchata.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EPollo%20Campero%20is%20not%20shy%20about%20taking%20on%20some%20of%20America's%20most%20prominent%20fast-food%20chicken%20brands%2C%20including%20Chick-fil-A.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pollo%20Campero%20introduced%20chicken%20sandwiches%20in%20the%20US%20states%20to%20compete%20with%20brands%20like%20Chick-fil-A.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6570b59b0ec98e92f74cc126%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Pollo%20Campero%20chicken%20sandwich%2C%20at%20top%2C%20compared%20with%20a%20Chick-fil-A%20sandwich.%20Pollo%20Campero%20introduced%20chicken%20sandwiches%20in%20the%20US%20in%202021%20and%202022.%20No%20doubt%2C%20they%20wanted%20a%20piece%20of%20action%20when%20it%20came%20to%20the%20chicken%20sandwich%20wars.%20%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBlas%20Escarcega%2C%20Pollo%20Campero's%20director%20of%20franchise%20development%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20chain's%20US%20division%20often%20opens%20stores%20right%20next%20to%20rivals%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fbest-fried-chicken-popeyes-churchs-chick-fil-a-kfc-2017-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPopeyes%20and%20Church's%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEscarcega%20said%20the%20brand's%20unique%20menu%20and%20service%20style%20(dine-in%20guests%20eat%20meals%20served%20on%20melamine%20plates)%20set%20itself%20apart%20from%20other%20chicken%20concepts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20truly%20believe%20that%20we%20have%20flavorful%20chicken%20meals%20with%20unique%20sides.%20It's%20something%20you're%20not%20going%20to%20get%20as%20far%20as%20a%20flavor%20profile%20in%20some%20of%20the%20other%20concepts%2C%20whether%20it's%20Popeyes%20or%20Church's%2C%26quot%3B%20Escarcega%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20a%20recent%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20chain%20plans%20to%20triple%20its%20US%20locations%20to%20250%20restaurants%20by%202026.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pollo%20Campero%20food%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6570b5f10ec98e92f74cc166%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPollo%20Campero%20sells%20a%20variety%20of%20menu%20options%20that%20can%20be%20found%20at%20different%20fast%20food%20chains%20such%20as%20Chipotle%2C%20KFC%2C%20and%20Chick-fil-A.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20wealthy%20Guatemalan%20family%20behind%20Pollo%20Campero%20plan%20to%20invest%20%24190%20million%20over%20the%20next%20three%20years%20on%20the%20chain's%20US%20expansion%2C%20Escarcega%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20identified%20several%20key%20markets%20for%20developing%20company-owned%20and%20franchised%20stores%2C%20including%20California%2C%20New%20York%2C%20Texas%2C%20Washington%20DC%2C%20Illinois%2C%20Boston%2C%20Nevada%2C%20and%20Atlanta%2C%20Georgia%2C%20South%20Carolina%2C%20North%20Carolina%2C%20Louisiana%2C%20Tennessee%2C%20northern%20Florida%2C%20Arizona%2C%20Utah%2C%20and%20Colorado.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20visited%20Pollo%20Campero%20in%20Santa%20Ana%2C%20California.%20The%20menu%20was%20so%20big%20I%20had%20to%20go%20twice%20to%20try%20all%20the%20dishes.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pollo%20Camero's%20dining%20room.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6570b89658e7c0c29a2a43ba%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThis%20Pollo%20Campero%20in%20Santa%20Ana%2C%20California%2C%20took%20over%20a%20closed%20KFC%20location.%20It%20looks%20much%20nicer.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20restaurant%2C%20which%20took%20over%20a%20closed%20KFC%20location%2C%20was%20near%20Target.%20It's%20also%20down%20the%20street%20from%20a%20Popeyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEscarcega%20said%20the%20chain%20likes%20to%20plant%20itself%20in%20high-traffic%20retail%20locations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20dining%20room%20had%20a%20mix%20of%20high-top%20tables%2C%20booths%2C%20and%20standard%20tables%20with%20chairs.%20Each%20table%20had%20plenty%20of%20eating%20space%2C%20clearly%20designed%20for%20family-style%20eating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOn%20my%20first%20visit%2C%20I%20didn't%20try%20the%20bone-in%20fried%20chicken.%20I%20was%20told%20that%20was%20a%20%26quot%3BCampero%20sin.%26quot%3B%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pollo%20Campero's%20bone-in%20fried%20chicken%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6570b8d47a3c8094d5da442a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPollo%20Campero's%20bone-in%20fried%20chicken%20is%20considered%20the%20hero%20product%20on%20the%20menu.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hero%20of%20the%20menu%20is%20the%20chain's%20thinly%20breaded%2C%20pressure-cooked%20bone-in%20chicken.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20didn't%20try%20it%20on%20my%20first%20visit%20because%20I%20was%20comparing%20the%20brand%20to%20Chick-fil-A%2C%20which%20doesn't%20sell%20bone-in%20chicken.%20(You%20can%20read%20that%20review%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpollo-campero-the-little-known-fast-food-brand-taking-us-by-storm-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20interviewed%20Escarcega%20a%20few%20days%20after%20my%20first%20visit.%20He%20is%20based%20in%20Pollo%20Campero's%20US%20headquarters%20in%20Dallas%2C%20Texas.%20He%20told%20me%20I%20committed%20a%20%26quot%3BCampero%20sin%26quot%3B%20for%20not%20having%20the%20fried%20chicken.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20I%20returned%20to%20the%20restaurant%20two%20weeks%20later%20for%20absolution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wanted%20to%20see%20if%20the%20chicken%20was%20better%20than%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkfc-vs-popeyes-fried-chicken-review-taste-test-photos-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPopeyes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20I%20prefer%20over%20KFC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20chicken%20sandwich%20wasn't%20a%20good%20first%20impression%20of%20the%20brand's%20proprietary%20fried%20chicken.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20best%20part%20of%20the%20classic%20chicken%20sandwich%20at%20Campero%20was%20the%20hefty%20chicken%20breast%2C%20and%20the%20crunchy%20pickle.%20That's%20it.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65677358fe5bc6545ebd643e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20classic%20chicken%20sandwich%20at%20Campero%20contained%20a%20sizable%20piece%20of%20fried%20chicken.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20may%20have%20committed%20a%20sin%20by%20not%20ordering%20the%20bone-in%20fried%20chicken%2C%20but%20shouldn't%20the%20flavor%20profile%20of%20the%20lightly%20coated%20breading%20be%20the%20same%20in%20the%20chicken%20sandwich%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20it%20was%2C%20I%20wasn't%20at%20all%20impressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chicken%2C%20as%20I%20stated%20in%20my%20previous%20review%2C%20was%20boring.%20No%20flavor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20spicy%20chicken%20sandwich%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20was%20crazy%20good.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20adding%20spices%20to%20the%20breading%2C%20Campero%20brings%20up%20the%20heat%20in%20this%20sandwich%20by%20using%20a%20secret%20spicy%20sauce%20slathered%20on%20the%20bun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20manager%20told%20me%20it%20was%20a%20%26quot%3BCaribbean-style%26quot%3B%20dressing.%20It%20should%20be%20bottled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EPollo%20Campero%20takes%20dine-in%20presentation%20up%20a%20notch%20with%20its%20plating.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pollo%20Campero%20was%20founded%20in%20Guatemala%20in%201971.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6570b32c7a3c8094d5da3d3b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPollo%20Campero%20was%20founded%20in%20Guatemala%20in%201971.%20It%20is%20known%20for%20its%20fried%20chicken.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20immediately%20taken%20aback%20by%20Campero's%20presentation.%20Everything%20is%20served%20on%20melamine%20plates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEscarcega%20said%20this%20is%20how%20food%20is%20served%20in%20its%20core%20restaurants%20in%20Central%20America.%20He%20said%20the%20chain%20loves%20to%20serve%20food%20on%20real%20plates%20because%20that's%20how%20people%20eat%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20not%20want%20to%20go%20to%20my%20house%20and%20be%20served%20on%20a%20paper%20plate%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20nice%20touch%2C%20but%20if%20you're%20going%20to%20do%20that%20you%20should%20commit%20all%20the%20way.%20The%20chain%20provides%20plastic%20forks%20with%20the%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20chain%20serves%20an%20eclectic%20array%20of%20sides%2C%20such%20as%20yuca%20fries%20and%20macaroni%20and%20cheese.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221777%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20hero%20of%20the%20Pollo%20Campero%20menu%20is%20the%20chain's%20thinly-breaded%20pressure%20cooked%20bone-in%20chicken.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6570b9aa0ec98e92f74cc54d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPollo%20Campero%20offers%20an%20eclectic%20variety%20of%20sides.%3Cp%3EPollo%20Campero%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECampero's%20sides%20speak%20volumes%20about%20the%20brand's%20menu%20range.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20sell%20beans%2C%20rice%2C%20macaroni%20and%20cheese%2C%20coleslaw%2C%20french%20fries%2C%20yuca%20fries%2C%20and%20plantains.%20The%20chain's%20website%20lists%20mashed%20potatoes%20as%20a%20side%2C%20but%20it%20was%20not%20available%20at%20the%20restaurant%20I%20visited%20during%20both%20my%20visits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECampero%20added%20macaroni%20and%20cheese%20to%20the%20menu%20in%20the%20US%20in%20August.%20It%20is%20not%20served%20in%20Central%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEscarcega%20said%20the%20brand%20decided%20to%20add%20it%20because%20it's%20a%20%26quot%3Bmainstream%20side%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20US.%20The%20chicken%20sandwiches%20are%20also%20a%20US-only%20offering%2C%20debuting%20in%202021%20and%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20not%20a%20fan%20of%20the%20mac%20'n%20cheese.%20I%20thought%20Chick-fil-A's%20was%20better.%20Escarcega%20said%20the%20new%20dish%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bwell%20accepted%26quot%3B%20by%20customers.%20My%20cashier%20in%20Santa%20Ana%20also%20told%20me%20it%20was%20his%20favorite%20side%20dish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20tried%20all%20the%20sides%2C%20and%20I%20thought%20the%20best%20item%20was%20the%20Campero%20beans.%20They%20were%20addictive.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Campero%20beans%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6570bbda0ec98e92f74cc7f0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Campero%20beans%2C%20on%20the%20bottom%20right%20below%20the%20plate%2C%20are%20made%20with%20chorizo.%20They%20were%20addictive.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Campero%20beans%20are%20packed%20with%20flavor.%20The%20pinto%20beans%20are%20slow-roasted%20with%20chorizo%2C%20mild%20poblano%20chilies%2C%20chopped%20onions%2C%20and%20diced%20tomatoes.%20The%20spicy%20chorizo%20is%20the%20key%20component%20in%20this%20side%20dish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20scraping%20my%20bowl%20with%20a%20dinner%20roll%20to%20ensure%20I%20ingested%20every%20morsel%20of%20the%20dish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOn%20my%20second%20visit%2C%20I%20ordered%20the%20bone-in%20fried%20chicken.%20After%20eating%20it%2C%20I%20confess%20it%20was%20indeed%20a%20sin%20not%20to%20try%20it%20first.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pollo%20Campero's%20fried%20chicken.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6570bc9a58e7c0c29a2a47bd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20was%20told%20it%20was%20a%20%26quot%3BCampero%20sin%26quot%3B%20to%20visit%20a%20store%20and%20not%20try%20the%20fried%20chicken.%20The%20chicken%20is%20fried%20in%20palm%20oil.%20%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bone-in%20fried%20chicken%20definitely%20had%20thicker%20breading%20than%20the%20coating%20I%20tried%20on%20the%20chicken%20sandwiches.%20But%20it%20is%20not%20as%20thick%20as%20the%20breading%20on%20KFC%20and%20Popeyes%20bone-in%20chicken.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pressure-cooked%20chicken%2C%20which%20is%20marinated%20to%20the%20bone%2C%20was%20moist%20and%20juicy.%20It%20looked%20like%20pan-fried%20Southern%20fried%20chicken%20but%20with%20a%20slightly%20darker%20coating.%20The%20breading%20was%20crispy%20and%20full%20of%20flavor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20unlike%20KFC%20and%20Popeyes%2C%20it%20wasn't%20greasy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20bone-in%20chicken%20goes%2C%20Pollo%20Campero%20is%20far%20superior%20than%20KFC%2C%20and%20on%20par%20with%20Popeyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFor%20those%20who%20don't%20want%20fried%20chicken%2C%20Pollo%20Campero%20offers%20grilled%20bone-in%20chicken.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pollo%20Campero's%20grilled%20chicken%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6570bd350ec98e92f74cc8d1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPollo%20Campero%20grilled%20chicken%20is%20marinated%20with%20a%20citrus%20blend%20that%20is%20similar%20to%20El%20Pollo%20Loco.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20grilled%20chicken%20had%20a%20nice%20char%20on%20the%20outside.%20It%20presented%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20first%20bite%2C%20I%20could%20taste%20the%20zest%20of%20the%20citrus-marinade.%20But%2C%20that%20flavor%20profile%20disappeared%20on%20subsequent%20bites.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20good%2C%20but%20not%20as%20good%20as%20El%20Pollo%20Loco%2C%20which%20grills%20its%20chicken%20over%20an%20open%20flame.%20But%2C%20I%20like%20the%20fact%20that%20Campero%20is%20offering%20a%20non-fried%20chicken%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ECampero's%20chicken%20bowl%20and%20chicken%20salad%20look%20almost%20identical.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Campero%20salad%20and%20bowl%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6570c0d258e7c0c29a2a4bc4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22360%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Pollo%20Campero%20salad%2C%20bottom%2C%20and%20bowl%20look%20similar.%20%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20El%20Pollo%20Loco%20and%20Chipotle%2C%20Pollo%20Campero%20offers%20a%20bowl%20and%20a%20salad%20for%20those%20who%20don't%20want%20to%20get%20their%20hands%20messy%20with%20bone-in%20fried%20chicken%20or%20grilled%20chicken.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bowl%20is%20on%20a%20bed%20of%20rice%20topped%20with%20Campero%20beans%2C%20spring%20mix%2C%20roasted%20corn%20and%20peppers%2C%20cherry%20tomatoes%2C%20smashed%20avocado%2C%20and%20feta%20cheese.%20It%20is%20topped%20with%20bite-size%20chunks%20of%20fried%20chicken.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20salad%20is%20a%20bed%20of%20spring%20mix%20topped%20fried%20chicken%2C%20roasted%20corn%20and%20peppers%2C%20shredded%20carrots%2C%20grape%20tomatoes%2C%20and%20feta%20cheese.%20The%20dressing%20options%20include%20ranch%20or%20Paul%20Newman's%20balsamic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bowl%20was%20my%20favorite%20of%20the%20two%20because%20it%20was%20a%20heartier%20meal%20with%20the%20warm%20rice%20and%20the%20delicious%20Campero%20beans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20most%20unique%20entree%20on%20the%20menu%20was%20the%20empanada.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pollo%20Campero's%20empanada.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6570d23b7a3c8094d5da5d24%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPollo%20Campero's%20empanada%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20served%20with%20sauce.%20We%20didn't%20get%20any.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20empanada%20is%20described%20as%20being%20stuffed%20with%20%26quot%3Bfreshly%20pulled%20chicken%2C%20roasted%20corn%2C%20peppers%2C%20onion%2C%20and%20Monterey%20Jack%20cheese.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20served%20with%20the%20chain's%20tangy%20Campero%20sauce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20the%20sauce%20was%20missing.%20And%2C%20we%20really%20needed%20sauce%20for%20this%20dish.%20The%20empanada's%20exterior%20texture%20was%20not%20crispy.%20It%20was%20limp%2C%20and%20chewy.%20It%20tasted%20more%20like%20a%20spicy%20chicken%20dumpling.%20But%20the%20pulled%20chicken%20was%20very%20tasty.%20I%20wish%20the%20pulled%20chicken%20was%20an%20option%20for%20the%20bowl%20or%20salad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ELast%20but%20not%20least%2C%20Campero%20serves%20two%20desserts%3A%20a%20chocolate%20chip%20cookie%20and%20flan.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pollo%20Campero%20desserts%20include%20flan%20and%20chocolate%20chip%20cookies.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6570c2377a3c8094d5da4dc2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPollo%20Campero%20desserts%20include%20flan%20and%20chocolate%20chip%20cookies.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20I%20admire%20about%20this%20brand%20is%20they%20cast%20a%20wide%20net.%20They%20are%20not%20shy%20about%20trying%20to%20appeal%20to%20various%20palates.%20Not%20everyone%20likes%20flan.%20But%20most%20everyone%20loves%20chocolate%20chip%20cookies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20desserts%20are%20better%20than%20most%20fast%20food%20offerings.%20(Chick-fil-A%20shakes%20excluded).%20The%20slightly%20chewy%20cookie%2C%20packed%20with%20lots%20of%20chocol