%20improved%20relations%20with%20India%20and%20other%20neighbouring%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20have%20to%20improve%20our%20relations%20with%20India%2C%20Afghanistan%2C%20and%20Iran.%20We%20need%20to%20make%20more%20stronger%20relations%20with%20China%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sharif%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20regretted%20that%20Pakistan%20lagged%20behind%20its%20neighbours%20in%20economic%20growth%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELashing%20out%20at%20Pakistan%20Tehreek-e-Insaf%20party's%20jailed%20former%20chairman%20Imran%20Khan%2C%20Mr%20Sharif%20said%20he%20did%20not%20know%20why%20an%20inexperienced%20man%20was%20given%20the%20reins%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20economy%20witnessed%20a%20downfall%20during%20Imran%20Khan's%20government%20(2018-2202).%20Then%20the%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%20government%20took%20over%20in%20April%202022%20and%20rescued%20the%20country%20from%20default.%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sharif%20reiterated%20his%20demand%20for%20accountability%20of%20former%20military%20generals%20and%20judges%20for%20ruining%20the%20country%20by%20ousting%20his%20government%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20who%20brought%20this%20country%20to%20this%20level%20should%20be%20made%20accountable%20as%20patriotic%20people%20can't%20do%20this%20to%20their%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20Mr%20Sharif%20had%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20do%20not%20want%20to%20come%20into%20power%20to%20roam%20around%20in%20luxury%20cars%20but%20we%20want%20accountability%20of%20those%20(who)%20ruined%20this%20country%20and%20made%20false%20cases%20against%20us.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20month%20before%20his%20return%20to%20Pakistan%20after%20four%20years%20of%20self-imposed%20exile%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20Mr%20Sharif%20had%20hinted%20at%20bringing%20former%20army%20chief%20Gen%20Qamar%20Javed%20Bajwa%2C%20former%20ISI%20head%20Lt-Gen%20Faiz%20Hamid%2C%20and%20former%20chief%2