xologist%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Da5aadd3f2a3270953da4363553b77db148b1692c741675ed76830c7b652e3dc6%26postID%3D6566444cbb2875d248bf494e%26postSlug%3Dhow-to-have-good-threesome-sex-expert-tips-positions-2023-12%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.goodvibes.com%252Fs%252Fcontent%252Fc%252Fgood-vibrations-sexologist-carol-queen%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EGood%20Vibes%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20curator%20of%20the%20Antique%20Vibrator%20Museum%2C%20said%20%26quot%3Bthree%20people%20who%20are%20comfortable%20with%20sexuality%2C%20can%20communicate%20well%2C%20are%20attracted%20enough%20to%20each%20other%20to%20be%20sexual%20together%26quot%3B%20are%20the%20best%20group%20for%20a%20threesome.%20All%20partners%20should%20%26quot%3Bhave%20compatible%20interests%20and%20boundaries%20to%20have%20a%20good%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20to%20find%20a%20third%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fpartner-and-i-had-first-threesome-open-relationship-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emonogamous%20%3C%2Fa%3Erelationship%2C%20finding%20who%20to%20add%20as%20a%20third%20party%20can%20be%20a%20big%20decision.%20Queen%20advises%20to%20%26quot%3Bskip%20the%20friend%20option%20unless%20you%20have%20a%20friend%20who%20is%20an%20open%20and%20openhearted%20sex%20explorer%20%E2%80%94%20a%20friend%20like%20that%20might%20actually%20love%20to%20take%20you%20under%20their%20wing.%26quot%3B%20Queen%20added%20that%20inviting%20a%20friend%20over%20and%20propositioning%20them%20is%20a%20big%20no-no.%20Open%20and%20honest%20communication%20will%20be%20critical%20to%20ensure%20the%20health%20of%20the%20friendship%20long-term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20not%20sure%20where%20to%20find%20a%20third%2C%20Suzannah%20Weiss%2C%20resident%20sexologist%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgetfleshy.com%2Fus-sp-pro.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EFleshy%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20suggested%20joining%20apps%20like%20Feeld%20or%20Bloom%2C%20which%20are%20%26quot%3Bgeared%20toward%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fpartner-and-i-had-first-threesome-open-relationship-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Enon-monogamous%20community%2C%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20you%20can%20mention%20that%20you%20are%20new%20to%20this%20and%20need%20some%20time%20to%20get%20to%20know%20people%20before%20jumping%20into%20bed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20right%20position%20will%20vary%20with%20each%20threesome%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20some%20positions%20may%20be%20more%20conducive%20to%20a%20threesome%20than%20others%2C%20not%20every%20position%20will%20work%20in%20every%20configuration%2C%20and%20it's%20important%20to%20communicate%20with%20partners%20about%20what%20will%20work%20for%20you%2C%20according%20to%20sexologist%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.holisticwisdom.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ELisa%20Lawless%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20sex%20positions%20are%20more%20accessible%20if%20you're%20a%20certain%20height%20or%20weight%20or%20are%20particularly%20strong%20or%20flexible%2C%26quot%3B%20Lawless%20said.%20The%20best%20position%20will%20depend%20on%20the%20type%20of%20sexual%20stimulation%20one%20wishes%20to%20receive%20or%20provide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELawless%20suggested%20the%20following%20positions%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EDouble%20cowgirl%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20double%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fsex-relationships%2Fcowgirl-sex-position%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecowgirl%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20one%20partner%20rides%20on%20the%20partner's%20genitals%20while%20the%20other%20rides%20that%20person's%20face.%20In%20this%20position%2C%20Lawless%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20person%20on%20the%20bottom%20gets%20stimulation%20from%20both%20partners%20simultaneously.%20For%20many%2C%20watching%20