tine%20cleaning%20on%20Wednesday%20morning%20after%20staff%20spotted%20one%20of%20the%20tigers%20with%20a%20shoe%20in%20its%20mouth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20reportedly%20jumped%20into%20the%20tiger%20enclosure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20circumstances%20surrounding%20the%20attack%2C%20believed%20to%20have%20occurred%20late%20Tuesday%20night%2C%20are%20under%20investigation.%20The%20victim%2C%20yet%20to%20be%20identified%2C%20is%20speculated%20to%20have%20been%20alive%20during%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20zoo%20is%20closed%20right%20now%20as%20we%20determine%20how%20the%20man%20got%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ali%20Usman%20Bukhari%2C%20a%20senior%20officer%20of%20the%20province's%20wildlife%20department%2C%20which%20operates%20the%20zoo%2C%20per%20CBS%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Bahawalpur%20Zoo%20in%20Punjab%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbahawalpur.punjab.gov.pk%2Fbwp-zoo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emanaged%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20Pakistan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20according%20to%20the%20zoo's%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20autopsy%20report%20has%20not%20been%20released%2C%20however%20evidence%20gathered%20from%20the%20enclosure%20points%20towards%20him%20being%20alive%20when%20he%20was%20attacked%20by%20the%20tigers%2C%26quot%3B%20Bukhari%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBukhari%20pledged%20to%20address%20any%20security%20lapses%20and%20consider%20hiring%20private%20security%20guards%20if%20necessary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESenior%20local%20government%20official%20Zaheer%20Anwar%2C%20speaking%20to%20the%20media%20outside%20the%20zoo%2C%20expressed%20initial%20assessments%20that%20the%20victim%20may%20have%20been%20acting%20irrationally%2C%20per%20CBS%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20assessment%20so%20far%20is%20that%20this%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20lunatic%2C%20because%20a%20sensible%20person%20would%20not%20jump%20into%20the%20den%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20remarked%2C%20pointing%20out%20the%20secured%20nature%20of%20the%20enclosure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20tigers%20reportedly%20involved%20in%20the%20incident%20have%20been%20confined%20to%20a%20smaller%20space%20while%20authorities%20collect%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESherbagh%20Zoo%2C%20established%20in%201942%20by%20the%20ruling%20royal%20family%20of%20Bahawalpur%2C%20features%20modern%20moated%20enclosures%20for%20lions%2C%20tigers%2C%20and%20hyenas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPakistani%20zoos%20have%20often%20faced%20criticism%20for%20their%20poor%20conditions%20and%20alleged%20neglect%20of%20animal%20welfare.%20In%202020%2C%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-51653984%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20remains%20of%20a%20missing%20teenage%20boy%20were%20discovered%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20lion%20enclosure%20of%20a%20zoo%20in%20Lahore%2C%20per%20the%20BBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDamning%20reports%20have%20also%20been%20made%20against%20a%20zoo%20in%20Karachi%2C%20the%20largest%20city%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20Deutsche%20Welle%20reports.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fpakistan-karachi-zoo-struggles-to-feed-animals-amid-financial-turmoil%2Fa-65228791%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eanimals%20are%20allegedly%20malnourished%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20kept%20in%20cramped%20enclosures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWWF%20wrote%20that%20there%20are%20%26quot%3Bmany%20animal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wwfpak.org%2Fknowledge_hub_%2Fposition_papers%2Fposition_on_zoos_in_pakistan_%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewelfare%20issues%20in%20captive%20facilities%20in%20Pakistan%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fman-mauled-to-death-by-tigers-in-pakistan-zoo-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702116025000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657341b358e7c0c29a2b074a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.