mitted%20an%20application%20to%20set%20up%20a%20semiconductor%20processing%20plant%20in%20Assam%20with%20an%20investment%20of%20Rs%2040%2C000%20crore.%20This%20will%20be%20a%20game-changer.%20My%20gratitude%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20for%20his%20continuous%20guidance%20in%20transforming%20our%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sarma%20had%20announced%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chidambaram%20today%20reposted%20the%20announcement%20on%20his%20own%20X%20timeline%20-%20and%20added%20a%20request.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCall%20me%20when%20the%20facility%20is%20actually%20operational%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chidambaram%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Himanta%2C%20indicating%20he%20was%20up%20for%20the%20challenge%2C%20responded%2C%20%26quot%3BYes.%20I%20will.%20Promise.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EYes%20.%20I%20will%20.%20Promise%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F9i8AxgNbms%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F9i8AxgNbms%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20(%40himantabiswa)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhimantabiswa%2Fstatus%2F1733392036924108823%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%209%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20MP's%20post%20was%20seen%20as%20a%20swipe%20at%20Mr%20Sarma's%20announcement%20of%20the%20massive%20project.%20Mr%20Chidambaram's%20tweet%20on%20the%20completion%20of%20the%20semiconductor%20project%20was%20also%20seen%20as%20alluding%20to%20failure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sarma%20has%20said%20he%20is%20working%20on%20policies%20to%20make%20the%20youth%20of%20Assam%20self-reliant.%20The%20Chief%20Minister's%20Atmanirbhar%20Assam%20Abhiyan%20was%20launched%20on%20September%2023%2C%20under%20which%20two%20lakh%20youth%20will%20be%20empowered%20to%20start%20entrepreneur%20ventures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20beneficiaries%2