ated%20by%20some%20leaders%20in%20the%20Congress%20and%20its%20allies%20as%20the%20trailer%20of%20what's%20in%20store%20for%20the%20battle%20of%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20%26quot%3BSouth%20of%20India%20being%20BJP%20mukt%26quot%3B%20-%20as%20claimed%20by%20some%20opposition%20leaders%20-%20the%20stage%20is%20set%20for%20a%20battle%20between%20the%20North%20and%20the%20South%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20the%20election%20results%2C%20DMK%20MP%20Senthilkumar%20made%20a%20controversial%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Egaumutra%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%C2%A0comment%20in%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20later%20apologized%20and%20the%20comments%20were%20expunged.%20Karti%20Chidambaram%2C%20the%20son%20of%20P%20Chidambaram%2C%20proclaimed%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20SOUTH!%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chairman%20of%20Congress'%20data%20analytic%20department%2C%20Praveen%20Chakravarty%2C%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20South-North%20boundary%20line%20is%20getting%20thicker%20%26amp%3B%20clearer!%26quot%3B%20He%20subsequently%20deleted%20the%20post%2C%20but%20screenshots%20remain%20readily%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20people%20advocating%20this%20theory%20of%20%26quot%3BNorth%20versus%20South%26quot%3B%20battle%20in%202024%20give%20the%20example%20of%20the%201977%20general%20elections%20when%20the%20Congress%20which%20was%20wiped%20out%20in%20the%20North%20by%20the%20Janata%20Party%2C%20but%20held%20onto%20its%20fort%20in%20the%20South.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20154%20Congress%20MPs%20elected%2C%2094%20were%20from%20the%20southern%20states%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Kerala%2C%20Karnataka%20and%20UTs%20Andaman%20and%20Lakshadweep.%20The%20Janata%20Party%20could%20win%20only%20three%20seats%20in%201977.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Southern%20part%20of%20India%20sends%20132%20MPs%20to%20Lok%20Sabha%20(1%2F4th%20of%20its%20overall%20strength)%3A%20Telangana%20(17)%2C%20Andhra%20(25)%2C%20Karnataka%20(28)%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20(39)%2C%20Kerala%20(20)%2C%20and%20Puducherry%2C%20Andaman%20and%20Nicobar%20Islands%2C%20Lakshadweep%20one%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20party%20and%20its%20allies%20of%20UPA%20(DMK%2C%20CPI%2C%20CPM%20etc)%20have%20already%20maxed%20out%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20winning%2037%20of%20the%2039%20seats%20on%20offer%20in%202019.%20In%20Kerala%2C%20Congress%20won%2019%20of%20the%2020%20seats%20on%20offer.%20So%20there%20is%20no%20scope%20for%20improvement%20there%2C%20losses%20cannot%20be%20ruled%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Telangana%20in%202019%2C%20BRS%20won%20nine%2C%20the%20BJP%20four%2C%20Congress%20three%20and%20the%20AIMIM%20one%20seat.%20The%20state%20elections%20have%20given%20hope%20to%20the%20Congress%20to%20better%20its%20performance%20in%202024.%20While%20the%20Congress%20recorded%20a%2039.4%25%20vote%20share%2C%20the%20BRS%20still%20has%2037.4%25%2C%20and%20the%20BJP%2013.9%25%20showing%20a%20triangular%20fight%20cannot%20be%20ruled%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Congress%20supporters%20hope%20this%20could%20have%20a%20rub%20off%20impact%20on%20Andhra%2C%20it%20seems%20like%20a%20wish%20list%20at%20this%20moment.%20In%20both%20state%20and%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20Congress%20party%20has%20been%20reduced%20to%20a%20nought%20with%20less%20than%201.5%25%20vote%20share.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnless%20it%20allies%20with%20the%20TDP%2C%20it%20cannot%20hope%20for%20a%20miracle%20there.%20However%2C%20the%20question%20is%20why%20the%20TDP%20would%20seek%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20Congress%2C%20as%20it%20has%20been%20making%20overtures%20to%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Karnataka%2C%20riding%20on%20its%20impressive%20victory%20in%20state%20elections%2C%20the%20party%20hopes%20to%20make%20substantial%20gains%20banking%20on%20its%20Vokkaliga%20and%20AHINDA%20(an%20acronym%20of%20minorities%2C%20backward%20classes%20and%20Dalits)%20coalition%20and%20the%20delivery%20of%20its%20promises.%20In%201999%2C%20the%20Congress%20party%20had%20won%2018%20of%20the%2028%20seats%20on%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20since%202004%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20led%20in%20all%20four%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20in%20this%20century%20so%20far%2C%20winning%20the%20maximum%20number%20of%20seats.%20With%20BS%20Yediyurappa's%20son%20as%20state%20president%2C%20it%20hopes%20to%20bring%20back%20the%20Lingayat%20voters%2C%20and%20negate%20some%20losses%20of%20state%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20it%20is%20not%20going%20to%20be%20a%20cakewalk%20for%20the%20Congress%20in%20these%20132%20seats%2C%20of%20which%20it%20had%20won%2063%20seats%20in%202019%2C%20along%20with%20its%20allies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20or%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20cannot%20hope%20to%20win%202024%20only%20banking%20on%20the%20South%2C%20as%20other%20regions%20account%20for%2075%25%20of%20seat%20strength.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20party%20and%20the%20BJP%20were%20locked%20in%20a%20direct%20contest%20in%20190%20seats%20in%202019%2C%20of%20which%20the%20BJP%20won%20175%20and%20Congress%20only%2015.%20115%20of%20these%20seats%20(60%25)%20are%20in%20North%20India.%20The%20state%20elections%202023%20results%20show%20that%20Congress%20could%20struggle%20to%20win%20these%20seats%2C%20as%20it%20lacks%20the%20narrative%20and%20leadership%20to%20match%20the%20BJP%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20these%20seats%2C%20regional%20parties%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20have%20a%20limited%20role%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20even%20tougher%20for%20the%20grand%20old%20party.%20It%20is%20here%20where%20the%20sanatan%20dharma%2C%20and%20the%20recent%20gaumutra%20remarks%20are%20politically%20damaging%20for%20the%20Congress%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DMK%20may%20not%20take%20flak%20for%20this%20as%20it%20is%20not%20present%20outside%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Puducherry%20-%20just%2040%20seats%20-%20but%20the%20Congress%20has%20to%20contest%2C%20even%20in%20the%20worst%20case%2C%20250%20to%20300%20seats%2C%20and%20it%20would%20have%20to%20bear%20the%20consequences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20could%20drive%20the%20narrative%20that%20when%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20talking%20of%20inclusiveness%2C%20the%20Congress%20is%20talking%20of%20dividing%20the%20society%20on%20caste%20and%20religious%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20fact%20that%20southern%20states%20have%20higher%20per%20capita%20income%20is%20correct%2C%20the%20key%20to%20the%20chains%20of%20power%20in%20Delhi%20run%20through%20the%20north%2C%20and%20it%20will%20be%20political%20harakiri%20to%20make%202024%20a%20%26quot%3Bnorth%20versus%20south%26quot%3B%20battle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702111200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F5tnc6udo_rahul-gandhi-mallikarjun-kharge-ani_625x300_08_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fnorth-south-divide-risky-strategy-for-congress-in-2024-4648827%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%203-1%20scoreline%20of%20state%20elections%202023%20has%20been%20extrapolated%20by%20some%20leaders%20in%20the%20Congress%20and%20its%20allies%20as%20the%20trailer%20of%20what's%20in%20store%20for%20the%20battle%20of%202024.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fnorth-south-divide-risky-strategy-for-congress-in-2024-4648827%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fnorth-south-divide-risky-strategy-for-congress-in-2024-4648827%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2F