ked%20On%20Congress%20Campaign%20In%20Rajasthan.%20Here's%20Why%20We%20Lost%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EI%20worked%20as%20a%20campaign%20manager%20for%20the%20Congress%20party%20in%20the%202023%20Rajasthan%20assembly%20elections.%20I%20want%20to%20put%20on%20record%20some%20observations%20about%20the%20fascinating%20politics%20of%20this%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20greatest%20challenge%20this%20election%20was%20not%20the%20Bhartiya%20Janata%20Party%2C%20formidable%20as%20they%20are.%20Our%20greatest%20challenge%20was%20the%20inherent%20belief%20among%20a%20large%20section%20of%20voters%20that%20the%20government%20can%2C%20will%20and%20should%20change%20every%20five%20years.%20The%20saying%20is%2C%20we%20must%20turn%20the%20%3Cem%3Eroti%20%3C%2Fem%3Eor%20it%20will%20burn.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20tested%20this%20in%20a%20survey.%20A%20whopping%2073%25%20of%20respondents%20said%20they%20had%20heard%20of%20the%20term%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Eroti%20palatna%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B.%20A%20very%20large%20number%20of%20respondents%20-%2029%25%20of%20them%20-%20felt%20the%20tradition%20was%20so%20important%20that%20even%20if%20a%20government%20does%20well%2C%20it%20should%20be%20changed.%20When%20you%20can%20win%20or%20lose%20an%20election%20by%201-2%25%20vote%20share%2C%2029%25%20of%20people%20telling%20you%20that%20no%20amount%20of%20good%20governance%20can%20make%20them%20vote%20for%20you%20is%20a%20unique%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20same%20as%20%26quot%3Banti-incumbency%26quot%3B.%20From%20February%20onwards%2C%20our%20daily%20tracker%20survey%20consistently%20showed%20us%20that%20Chief%20Minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20and%20his%20government%20had%20very%20high%20ratings%20-%20surveys%20in%20the%20media%20before%20the%20elections%20found%20the%20same.%20Gehlot%20was%20consistently%20the%20favourite%20choice%20for%20Chief%20Minister%20across%20parties.%20People%20were%20happy%20with%20the%20Gehlot%20government%2C%20but%20the%20%3Cem%3Eroti%20%3C%2Fem%3Ealways%20turns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20was%20determined%20to%20change%20the%20tradition.%20We%20may%20have%20failed%20to%20do%20so%2C%20but%20we%20came%20very%20close.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EData%20gives%20us%20some%20sobering%20nuance%20to%20the%20tradition%20of%20alternation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20see%20that%20when%20it%20is%20the%20BJP's%20turn%20it%20usually%20wins%20big%2C%20both%20in%20terms%20of%20seats%20and%20vote%20share.%20When%20it%20is%20the%20Congress'%20turn%2C%20it%20usually%20just%20scrapes%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20charts%20below%20show%20you%20how%20the%20BJP's%20lead%20over%20the%20Congress%20was%20increasing%20over%20election%20cycles%20in%20the%202000s%2C%20in%20both%20seats%20and%20vote%20shares%2C%20but%20the%202023%20assembly%20election%20has%20pushed%20against%20the%20trend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%B8%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%A5%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A8%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B9%E0%A4%95%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%81%E0%A4%96%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%82%E0%A4%A4%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%85%E0%A4%B6%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%95%20%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%B9%E0%A4%B2%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%A4%20(%E0%A4%AB%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%87%E0%A4%B2%20%E0%A4%AB%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%9F%E0%A5%8B)%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%B8%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%A5%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A8%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B9%E0%A4%95%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%81%E0%A4%96%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%82%E0%A4%A4%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%85%E0%A4%B6%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%95%20%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%B9%E0%A4%B2%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%A4%20(%E0%A4%AB%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%87%E0%A4%B2%20%E0%A4%AB%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%9F%E0%A5%8B)%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F1349ao08_gfx-rajasthan-election_625x300_09_December_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%