t%20rankings%2C%20placing%20us%20second%20globally%20among%20the%20world's%20large-scale%20solar%20PV%20developers.%20This%20recognition%20underscores%20our%20continued%20and%20unwavering%20commitment%20as%20one%20of%20the%20fastest%20growing%20renewable%20energy%20players%20in%20the%20world%20and%20on%20target%20to%20achieving%20our%20ambitious%20goal%20of%2045%20GW%20renewable%20energy%20capacity%20by%202030.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EWe%20are%20happy%20to%20see%20Mercom%20Capital's%20recent%20rankings%2C%20placing%20us%20second%20globally%20among%20the%20world's%20large-scale%20solar%20PV%20developers.%20This%20recognition%20underscores%20our%20continued%20and%20unwavering%20commitment%20as%20one%20of%20the%20fastest%20growing%20renewable%20energy%20players%20in%20the%20world%20and%20on...%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Gautam%20Adani%20(%40gautam_adani)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgautam_adani%2Fstatus%2F1733317691115745778%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%209%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20top%20global%20solar%20developers%2C%20six%20were%20based%20in%20Europe%2C%20three%20in%20North%20America%2C%20and%20one%20was%20headquartered%20in%20South%20Asia.%20Project%20portfolios%20of%20the%20top%20developers%20were%20primarily%20located%20in%20North%20America%2C%20followed%20by%20Asia%20Pacific%2C%20Mercom%20Capital%20said%20in%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETotalEnergies%20was%20also%20the%20top%20company%20for%20under-construction%20and%20awarded%20(PPA-contracted)%20capacities%2C%20with%2029.3%20GW%20of%20projects.%20Brookfield%20Renewable%20Partners%20was%20the%20second-largest%20player%2C%20with%2013.6%20GW%2C%20followed%20by%20Adani%20Green%20Energy%20with%2011.1%20GW.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20year's%20report%20includes%20several%20new%20companies%2C%20primarily%20led%20by%20Eur