ntasy%20comedy%20film%20that%20brings%20to%20life%20the%20iconic%20dolls%20created%20by%20Mattel.%20The%20film%20promises%20a%20unique%20and%20captivating%20experience%20with%20a%20blend%20of%20fantasy%2C%20humor%2C%20and%20introspection.%20The%20stellar%20cast%20includes%20Margot%20Robbie%2C%20Ryan%20Gosling%2C%20America%20Ferrera%2C%20Kate%20McKinnon%2C%20Issa%20Rae%2C%20Rhea%20Perlman%2C%20and%20Will%20Ferrell.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fenglish%2Fmargot-robbies-barbie-to-make-ott-debut-on-december-21%2Farticleshow%2F105856923.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rinku%20Singh%20Reveals%20Message%20From%20Rahul%20Dravid%20Ahead%20Of%201st%20T20I%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20middle-order%20batter%20Rinku%20Singh%20feels%20the%20extra%20pace%20and%20bounce%20on%20offer%20on%20South%20African%20pitches%20will%20need%20a%20little%20more%20effort%20and%20practice%20to%20get%20used%20to.%20Giving%20his%20assessment%20about%20the%20South%20African%20wickets%20after%20India's%20first%20practice%20session%20here%2C%20Rinku%2C%20who%20played%20a%20vital%20role%20in%20India%20clinching%20the%20five-match%20T20I%20series%20series%20against%20Australia%20recently%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20battered%20here%20today%2C%20there%20was%20extra%20bounce%20here%20compared%20to%20Indian%20wickets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20pace%20is%20a%20bit%20more%2C%20so%20will%20practice%20against%20pace%20bowling.%26quot%3B%20India%20will%20play%20the%20first%20of%20their%20three%20T20Is%20against%20the%20Proteas%20here%20on%20Sunday%20and%20Rinku%20is%20expected%20to%20bat%20at%20the%20crucial%20No.%205%20or%20No.%206%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20head%20coach%20Rahul%20Dravid%20had%20also%20asked%20him%20to%20just%20play%20his%20natural%20game%20and%20bat%20at%20No.5%20or%20No.6.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20practice%20session%2C%20I%20enjoyed%20it%20a%20lot%20because%20of%20the%20fine%20weather.%20Getting%20the%20opportunity%20to%20work%20with%20Rahul%20Dravid%20sir%2C%20so%20that%20was%20a%20good%20feeling.%20He%20told%20me%20to%20continue%20playing%20the%20way%20I%20do%20and%20continue%20believing%20in%20myself%2C%26quot%3B%20Rinku%20told%20BCCI.tv.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B(He%20told%20me)%20to%20keep%20playing%20at%20No.%205%20or%206.%20It%20is%20tough%20to%20play%20in%20that%20position%2C%20but%20keep%20pushing%20yourself%20and%20believe%20in%20yourself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hard-hitter%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20added%20that%20batting%20in%20the%20two%20crucial%20positions%20since%202013%20had%20given%20him%20the%20confidence%20to%20play%20a%20similar%20role%20for%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20been%20playing%20for%20UP%20since%202013%20at%20No.%205%20or%206.%20So%2C%20I%20have%20got%20used%20to%20that%20position.%20I%20keep%20backing%20myself%20to%20play%20in%20that%20position%20because%20it%20is%20very%20tough%20to%20play%20in%20that%20position%20if%204-5%20wickets%20are%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20Rinku%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%20you%20have%20to%20build%20a%20partnership.%20So%20I%20keep%20telling%20myself%2C%20the%20more%20I%20can%20keep%20myself%20calm%2C%20the%20better%20it%20is%20(for%20me)%2C%20and%20not%20to%20react%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rinku.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20it%20is%20important%20to%20enjoy%20time%20out%20with%20fellow%20players%20to%20do%20well%20in%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%204-5%20players%20remain%20in%20a%20group.%20Me%2C%20Ravi%20(Bishnoi)%2C%20Arshdeep%20(Singh)%2C%20Avesh%20(Khan)%2C%20Jitesh%20(Sharma).%20We%20enjoy%20each%20other's%20company%2C%20which%20is%20very%20important%20in%20cricket.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20emphasised%20the%20need%20to%20remain%20fit%20in%20order%20to%20do%20well%20in%20cricket.