t%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08175443%2FUntitled-design-19.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EKolkata%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20picturesque%20town%20of%20Kurseong%20in%20West%20Bengal%20is%20currently%20bathed%20in%20fairy%20lights.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChristmas%20is%20still%20a%20few%20weeks%20away%2C%20but%20the%20hilly%20town%20is%20all%20lit%20up%20to%20celebrate%20the%20wedding%20of%20Abesh%20Banerjee%2C%20the%20nephew%20of%20West%20Bengal%20chief%20minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20with%20a%20local%20doctor.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Despite%20being%20a%20private%20affair%2C%20the%20wedding%20has%20stirred%20up%20controversy%20due%20to%20an%20administrative%20directive%20instructing%20medical%20professionals%20to%20attend%20to%20the%20healthcare%20needs%20of%20CM%20Banerjee%20and%20her%20heir%20apparent%2C%20Trinamool%20Congress%20MP%20Abhishek%20Banerjee.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20medical%20team%20comprising%20over%20100%20individuals%2C%20including%20specialist%20doctors%2C%20nurses%2C%20and%20general%20practitioners%20from%20North%20Bengal%2C%20has%20currently%20been%20deputed%20to%20two%20luxury%20resorts%20for%20the%20event.%20A%20circular%2C%20signed%20by%20the%20superintendent%20of%20Kurseong%20Sub-Divisional%20Hospital%20has%20been%20shared%20widely%20on%20social%20media.%20It%20has%20details%20on%20the%20medial%20team%20formed%20to%20cater%20to%20the%20VVIPs%20between%20December%204%20and%2010.%20The%20team%20includes%20specialists%20ranging%20from%20paediatricians%20to%20ophthalmologists.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20decision%20to%20divert%20medical%20resources%20and%20personnel%20for%20a%20private%20event%20has%20sparked%20criticism%20from%20opposition%20parties.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBJP%20leader%20Subhendu%20Adhikari%20commented%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20like%20a%20royal%20family%20wedding.%20Government%20doctors%20have%20been%20made%20to%20serve%20the%20royals%20of%20the%20state%2C%20having%20been%20taken%20away%20from%20their%20duty%20to%20serve%20the%20commoners.%20How%20does%20it%20matter%20to%20them%20that%20people%20are%20affected%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECommunist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%20leader%20Dr%20Sujan%20Chakraborty%20called%20this%20a%20gross%20abuse%20of%20power.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20many%20Z-category%20VIPs.%20But%20creating%20medical%20teams%20dedicated%20to%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20her%20nephew%20for%20seven%20days%20is%20unprecedented.%20The%20chief%20minister%20arrived%20in%20north%20Bengal%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20two%20days%20after%20the%20medical%20team%E2%80%99s%20deputation.%20What%20was%20the%20team%20doing%20there%20%5Bfor%20two%20days%5D%20when%20those%20who%20needed%20its%20services%20were%20being%20denied%20treatment%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETrinamool%20Congress%20spokesperson%20Kunal%20Ghosh%20has%20termed%20these%20allegations%20baseless.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20chief%20minister%20did%20not%20attend%20the%20wedding%20ritual%20but%20is%20staying%20at%20one%20of%20the%20resorts%20booked%20for%20the%20weeding.%20On%20Thursday%2C%20pictures%20of%20plucking%20teas%20while%20wearing%20local%20dress%20went%20viral%20on%20social%20media%20and%20were%20reported%20upon%20by%20Kolkata%20outlets%20too.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20diversion%20of%20medical%20resources%20for%20the%20VVIP%20wedding%20in%20Kurseong%20has%20triggered%20repercussions%20for%20the%20health%20system%20in%20the%20hills%2C%20compelling%20locals%20to%20seek%20medical%20attention%20in%20distant%20towns%20like%20Siliguri%20and%20Jalpaiguri%2C%20opposition%20has%20alleged.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08175956%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-12-08-at-11.58.55-AM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22791%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08175956%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-12-08-at-11.58.55-AM.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08175956%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-12-08-at-11.58.55-AM-300x225.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-688360%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22593%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20north%20Bengal%20hospital.%20Photo%3A%20By%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20many%20doctors%2C%20nurses%2C%20and%20health%20workers%20have%20been%20moved%20for%20seven%20days%20because%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20family%20wedding%20ceremony.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20people%20who%20used%20to%20get%20services%20in%20government%20hospitals%20are%20being%20turned%20away%20and%20told%20that%20they%20should%20return%20after%20seven%20days.%20Denying%20them%20treatment%20for%20a%20private%20family%20function%20is%20brutal%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Gautam%20Ghosh%2C%20a%20leader%20of%20the%20Chia%20Kaman%20Mazdoor%20Union%2C%20affiliated%20with%20Centre%20of%20Indian%20Trade%20Unions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EExpressing%20frustration%2C%20a%20doctor%20currently%20on%20duty%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20done%20my%20share%20of%20VVIP%20duty.%20But%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20accept%20that%20they%20brought%20us%20to%20this%20area%20because%20of%20the%20wedding%20of%20a%20member%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20family%20and%20will%20keep%20us%20like%20this%20for%20so%20long.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDr.%20Manas%20Gumta%2C%20secretary%20of%20the%20Association%20of%20Health%20Service%20Doctors%2C%20raised%20concerns%20abou