%20the%20demolition%20site.%20Fariha%20(29)%2C%20a%20domestic%20worker%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20know%20that%20the%20police%20are%20just%20following%20orders.%20We%20want%20to%20question%20the%20higher%20ups.%20Do%20we%20have%20no%20rights%3F%E2%80%9D%20Rani%20(26)%20objected%20to%20this%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20a%20problem%20with%20the%20police%20too%E2%80%A6%20they%20badly%20beat%20up%20a%20woman%20a%20few%20%3Cem%3Egalis%20%3C%2Fem%3Edown.%20Male%20policemen%20cannot%20hurt%20a%20woman%2C%20no%20matter%20what.%E2%80%9D%20The%20policy%20explicitly%20forbids%20violence%20against%20women%20and%20disabled%20people%20during%20the%20process%20of%20a%20demolition.%20It%20also%20mandates%20the%20DUSIB%20%E2%80%9Cshould%20ensure%20safe%20and%20affordable%20access%20to%20essential%20services%20%E2%80%93%20potable%20water%2C%20sanitation%20and%20health%E2%80%9D.%20Mohanty%20said%20that%20none%20of%20these%20services%20had%20been%20present%2C%20and%20temporary%20shelter%20and%20relief%20was%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20need%20of%20the%20hour%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08132018%2FSR7.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22904%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08132018%2FSR7.jpg%20904w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08132018%2FSR7-300x224.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-688281%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22676%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPolice%20personnel%20supervising%20the%20demolition%20keep%20a%20strict%20check%20on%20people%20going%20into%20and%20leaving%20the%20basti.%20Photo%3A%20Sukanya%20Roy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22