%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20we%20have%20designed%20is%20called%20an%20open-face%20console%2C%20featuring%20a%20large%2032-inch%204K%20high-definition%20resolution%203D%20monitor.%20This%20design%20enhances%20magnification%2C%20providing%20surgeons%20with%20the%20capability%20to%20perform%20procedures%20with%20exceptional%20precision.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20remarkable%20advancement%20for%20surgical%20procedures%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20he%20says%20they%20have%20integrated%20safety%20features%20with%20a%20head-tracking%20camera.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20surgeon%20wears%20glasses%20with%20specific%20markers%20that%20are%20tracked%20by%20the%20camera.%20This%20ensures%20that%20if%20the%20surgeon%20looks%20away%20from%20the%20monitor%2C%20even%20while%20moving%20their%20hands%2C%20the%20system%20will%20not%20respond.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20safety%20measure%20that%20requires%20the%20camera%20view%20to%20be%20within%20sight%20for%20operation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20technology%20also%20has%20a%2023-inch%20large%20monitor%20with%20all%20controls%20easily%20accessible%20to%20the%20surgeon.%20This%20allows%20the%20surgeon%20to%20retrieve%20any%20of%20the%20DICOM%20images%20from%20the%20server%2C%20whether%20in%20the%20radiology%20department%20or%20elsewhere%20in%20the%20hospital%20and%20display%20them%20conveniently.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20team%20has%20developed%20proprietary%20technology%20that%20enables%20them%20to%20convert%20these%20images%20into%203D%20models.%20Following%20this%2C%20a%20surgeon%20or%20a%20trainee%20can%20manipulate%20and%20slice%20through%20the%20images%2C%20essentially%20having%20the%20entire%20anatomy%20of%20the%20region%20you%E2%80%99re%20operating%20on%20right%20in%20front%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20not%20only%20makes%20the%20procedure%20safer%20and%20faster%20but%20also%20simplifies%20it%20by%20eliminating%20guesswork%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-5-1700577898.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Sudhir%20once%20sold%20his%20car%20and%20furniture%20to%20fund%20the%20research%20for%20the%20robot.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-5-1700577898.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-5-1700577898-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-5-1700577898-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-5-1700577898-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Frobot-5-1700577898-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334642%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Sudhir%20once%20sold%20his%20car%20and%20furniture%20to%20fund%20the%20research%20for%20the%20robot%3B%20Picture%20credit%3A%20SSI%20Innovations%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiving%20a%20real-life%20example%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20performing%20a%20surgical%20procedure%20in%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F263534%2Fanupath-tripathi-squid-game-netflix-facts-korean-drama-abdul-ali%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20South%20Korea%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%202008%2C%20a%20nurse%20accidentally%20inserted%20a%20knife%20right%20through%20the%20heart.%20When%20I%20inquired%20later%2C%20she%20explained%20that%20she%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20accurately%20gauge%20the%20depth.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20address%20problems%20like%20this%2C%20SSI%20Mantra%202%20provides%20a%20better%20view%20of%20the%20organ